This is Perl module Qpsmtpd::Plugin::EmailAddressLoose.

INSTALLATION

Qpsmtpd::Plugin::EmailAddressLoose installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % cpan Qpsmtpd::Plugin::EmailAddressLoose

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

Qpsmtpd::Plugin::EmailAddressLoose documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc Qpsmtpd::Plugin::EmailAddressLoose

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

